window.bookSummaryJSON = "<h4>WHEN IN DOUBT, WING IT.</h4><p><i>The Stellar Thief collects together the first four books in the Emberling series, a pulse-pounding, adrenaline-fueled space opera that will have you clinging to the edge of your seat!</i></p><p><b>Slim Taggart has stolen plenty of things in his short life.</b> That's what happens when you come from a family of planet-hopping thieves.</p><p>But when he somehow finds himself in possession of a shard from an ancient alien tech known as the Emberling, the heat is suddenly cranked up to scorching levels.</p><p>Before Taggart knows it, a half-dozen criminal syndicates are on his tail, desperate for the powerful payload.</p><p>And that's before he manages to take aboard a motley crew of characters who each openly admit they'd kill for it, too.</p><p>Luckily, Taggart has a plan. He always does.</p><p>He just hasn't quite figured out what it is yet...</p><p><b>Included in this box set:</b></p><ol><li><i>Exiled</i></li><li><i>Recoil</i></li><li><i>Surge</i></li><li><i>Valor</i></li></ol><p></p><p><b>Note: This series is a loving tribute to classic pulp sci-fi. If you're seeking hard sci-fi, you might want to search elsewhere. But for those who crave thrilling escapades on distant worlds teeming with bizarre alien lifeforms, look no further â€” the <i>Emberling</i> series awaits!</b></p>"; 
